      • updatePointValues

        public void updatePointValues(float minX,
                              float minY,
                              float left,
                              float bottom,
                              float ratioX,
                              float ratioY)
        Update all the points of the line. This method is call by LineChartView.notifyDataSetChanged()
        参数:
        minX - The min value of the X-axis
        minY - The min value of the Y-axis
        left - The left coordinate value of the X-axis
        bottom - The bottom coordinate value of the Y-axis
        ratioX - (right - left) / (maxX - minX)
        ratioY - (bottom - top) / (maxY - minY)
        另请参阅:
        PointValue
